<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="../File_Fire_1000_fps.ogg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="http://bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf8/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
