<li id="cite_note-27"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-27">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.firecomm.gov.mb.ca/safety_education_nero_and_ashcan.html#6">Fire &amp; Life Safety Education</a><sup class="noprint Inline-Template"><span title="&#160;since June 2011" style="white-space: nowrap;">[<i><a href="Wikipedia_Link_rot" title="Wikipedia:Link rot">dead link</a></i>]</span></sup>, <a href="Manitoba" title="Manitoba">Manitoba</a> Office of the Fire Commissioner</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-28"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-28">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.usfa.dhs.gov/citizens/atf/salvage.shtm">"US Department of Homeland Security, US Fire Administration Handbook"</a>. Usfa.dhs.gov. 2010-05-06<span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.usfa.dhs.gov/citizens/atf/salvage.shtm">http://www.usfa.dhs.gov/citizens/atf/salvage.shtm</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 2012-05-23</span>.</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-29"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-29">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation news">Begal, Bill (August 23, 2007). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.randrmagonline.com/CDA/Archives/BNP_GUID_9-5-2006_A_10000000000000156172">"Restoration With a Capital E-P-A: A Case Study"</a>. Restoration &amp; Remediation<span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.randrmagonline.com/CDA/Archives/BNP_GUID_9-5-2006_A_10000000000000156172">http://www.randrmagonline.com/CDA/Archives/BNP_GUID_9-5-2006_A_10000000000000156172</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 2008-04-11</span>.</span></span></li>
